-- ‘Harry Potter’ Actor Richard Griffiths Dies, Aged 65, PA Reports
-- B y   M i k e   H a r r i s o n
-- 2013-03-29T10:01:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-29/-harry-potter-actor-richard-griffiths-dies-aged-65-pa-reports.html
British actor Richard Griffiths,
who appeared in the “Harry Potter” film series, has died of
complications following heart surgery, the Press Association
said. He was 65.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
